text: René Benguerel (born 11 May 1973) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
